Astronomical data
================================================================

Stellar and exoplanet measurement values aggregated in `db/` are
derived from public astronomical catalogs (NASA Exoplanet Archive,
Gaia DR3, SIMBAD, TEPCat). These values are factual data and are
not subject to the repository's MIT license. Citation policies for
each catalog are documented in `docs/reference/data-sources.md`.
